#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.smb4k.appdata.xml:10
msgid "Smb4K"
msgstr "Smb4K"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.smb4k.appdata.xml:11
msgid "Discover and mount SAMBA and Windows shares over the network"
msgstr "Odkrijte in priklopite skupno rabo mrežnih diskov SAMBA in Windows"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.smb4k.appdata.xml:13
msgid ""
"Smb4K is an advanced network neighborhood browser and Samba share mounting "
"utility. It is based on the KDE Frameworks, QtKeychain, Samba's client "
"library (libsmbclient) and, optionally, the KDSoap WS-Discovery client. It "
"scans your network neighborhood for all available workgroups, servers and "
"shares and can mount all desired shares to your local file system."
msgstr ""
"Smb4K je napredni brskalnik sosedstva omrežja in pomožni program Samba za "
"priklop skupnih diskov. Temelji na ogrodju KDE Frameworks, QtKeychain "
"knjižnici odjemalcev Samba (libsmbclient) in neobvezno odjemalcu KDSoap WS-"
"Discovery. Pregleduje sosedstvo omrežja za vsem, kar je na voljo delovnih "
"skupin, strežnikov in delov diskov in kar lahko priklopite v vaš lokalni "
"sistem datotek."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.smb4k.appdata.xml:16
msgid "Features:"
msgstr "Zmožnosti:"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.smb4k.appdata.xml:20
msgid ""
"Scanning for (active) workgroups, hosts, and shares using Samba's client "
"library, DNS Service Discovery (DNS-SD) and, optionally, Web Services "
"Dynamic Discovery (WS-Discovery)"
msgstr ""
"Prečesavanje (aktivnih) delovnih skupin, gostiteljev in skupnih rab z "
"uporabo Sambine odjemalske knjižnice, DNS Service Discovery (DNS-SD) in "
"izbirino še Web Services Dynamic Discovery (WS-Discovery)"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.smb4k.appdata.xml:21
msgid ""
"Support of the CIFS and SMB3 file system under Linux as well as the SMBFS "
"file system under BSD"
msgstr ""
"Podpora datotečnemu sistemu CIFS in SMB3 pod Linuxom ter datotečnemu sistemu "
"SMBFS pod BSD"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.smb4k.appdata.xml:22
msgid "Mounting and unmounting of shares"
msgstr "Priklapljanje in odklapljanje skupnih diskov"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.smb4k.appdata.xml:23
msgid "Access to the files of a mounted share using a file manager or terminal"
msgstr ""
"Dostop do datotek diskov skupne rabe s pomočjo upravitelja datotek ali "
"terminala"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.smb4k.appdata.xml:24
msgid "Auto-detection of external mounts and unmounts"
msgstr "Samodejno zaznavanje zunanjih priklopov in odklopov"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.smb4k.appdata.xml:25
msgid "Remounting of previously used shares on program start"
msgstr ""
"Ponovno priklapljanje že prej priklopljenih skupnih diskov ob zagonu programa"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.smb4k.appdata.xml:26
msgid "Miscellaneous information about remote network items and mounted shares"
msgstr ""
"Razne informacije o oddaljenih omrežnih predmetih in priklopljenih skupnih "
